results.name: Spider-Man (Miles Morales)
results.description: Teenager Miles Morales grew up in Brooklyn, New York. Recently, Miles took on the controversial and pressured role of Spider-Man shortly after the death of the original. Morales made his debut against The Kangaroo, much to the surprise and disapproval of many present at the confrontation.

results.name: Spider-Man (Ultimate)
results.description: Peter’s relatively normal life changed abruptly during a school trip to Osborn Industries, Inc, where the company had been working on a super soldier serum, the Oz Compound; a spider exposed to it escaped and bit Peter before it was destroyed.

results.name: Spider-Woman (Mattie Franklin)
results.description: Mattie Franklin was granted her powers when, after overhearing a phone call between her father and Norman Osborn about the Gathering of the Five, she took her father's place during the Gathering and was endowed with the awesome powers that Norman Osborn had wanted for himself.
